edu.uwa.aidan.robot.world
Class Goal

java.lang.Object
  edu.uwa.aidan.robot.world.Goal

public class Goal
extends java.lang.Object

The Goal is what the Robot is searching for through the world. It is a circle, represented by a Ellipse2D with a radius of GOAL_RADIUS units. This implementation assumes that the Goal cannot move, further development could easily make this Goal move around the AgentWorld if desired.

Author:
Aidan Morgan
